# This project does NOT use .env files for secrets.
# All configuration is fetched from AWS SSM Parameter Store at runtime.
#
# Required SSM parameters (path: /banyan/hasura/):
#
# admin-token         — Pre-signed JWT for DDN Cloud auth (SecureString)
# db-connection-uri   — RDS PostgreSQL connection string (SecureString)
# rds-nlb-endpoint    — NLB DNS name for DDN Cloud RDS connectivity
#
# DDN Cloud secrets (set via DDN Console or ddn CLI):
#
# CONNECTION_URI      — RDS connection string via NLB endpoint
# JWT_SECRET_KEY      — HMAC key for JWT auth (from Secrets Manager banyan-prod-jwt-secret)
#
# Ensure your AWS credentials are configured:
#   AWS_PROFILE=banyan bun run hasura:tunnel
